<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7376> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7376" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator, brother of the poet C, Lucilius. Use of the cognomen Hirrus by no. 25, below, Tr. pl. 53, a descendant of the senatorial brother of the poet, and its occurrence in the epigram from Corinth that mentions a Hirrus as legatus pro praetore in 102-100 (MRR 1.569) suggest the name given above for the poet's brother. See Cichorius, RS 67-70; MRR 1.570, note 7.\n" .
